headline: Monster's International Markets Drive Strong Results
summary: Monster Beverage Corporation (NASDAQ: MNST) held its fourth-quarter and full-year 2024 earnings call on February 27, 2025.  During the call, leadership discussed their ongoing growth in global markets, pricing strategies, and challenges in the alcoholic beverage segment, which resulted in impairment charges.  Here are the most important insights for investors focused on Monster's long-term potential.
